        <text><![CDATA[ <p><strong>Office of Rural Telecommunications Act</strong></p> <p>This bill establishes the Office of Rural Telecommunications to help coordinate federal efforts and resources to develop rural telecommunications systems and to measure broadband adoption rates in rural areas.</p>]]></text>
